{"tid":351366,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"富士康副總裁：iPhone 8好撚貴 因螢幕良率只有60%","createTime":"2017-08-08T03:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T13:55:07.000Z","uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4c516628c878ce5c852f72cee18fc548cf7c347","tid":351366,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T03:36:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/08/08/foxconn-exec-explain-why-iphone-8-is-expensive/?utm_source=fbpost&amp;utm_medium=fb&amp;utm_campaign=nmlapple\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2Ffoxconn-exec-explain-why-iphone-8-is-expensive%2F%3Futm_source%3Dfbpost%26utm_medium%3Dfb%26utm_campaign%3Dnmlapple&d=t%2BWyz07Ewekxg3Ao4U6eyYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=62bac8b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/08/08/foxconn-exec-explain-why-iphone-8-is-expensive/?utm_source=fbpost&amp;utm_medium=fb&amp;utm_campaign=nmlapple</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n富士康副總裁爆料！解釋 iPhone 8 並不便宜的最大原因！<br />\n    <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\niPhone 8 將徹底重新設計螢幕，從 HomePod 的數據之中可以看到 iPhone 8 凹入螢幕的樣子，不過有富士康的極高層透露，因為一些複雜的原因，iPhone 8 並不便宜。<br />\n<br />\n富士康資深副總裁兼 Sharp 手機全球 CEO 羅忠生在微博曾經發出過一篇帖子（該帖子已被刪除），表面上爆料 iPhone 8 的發佈時間，但實際上講到「異形 OLED」螢幕的問題，他提到「異形 OLED」螢幕的良率只有 60%，原因是切割難度非常大，就因為這個問題，iPhone 8「並不便宜」。有關「異形 OLED」螢幕的產能問題，他在 7 月尾以微博文章解釋過，他指在無邊框手機流行之下，不少廠商仍尋找解決方案，Samsung 為 Galaxy S8 採用的是保留上下邊框的 edge-to-edge 螢幕，屬傳統手機螢幕改良，但 iPhone 8 的螢幕是屬於「異形」，異形切割非常困難，能量產的只有富士康旗下的 Sharp。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/113438_5bb3b2dc83df341da2dae5432b4f3a22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F113438_5bb3b2dc83df341da2dae5432b4f3a22.jpg&h=4aa53cde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAdv <br />\n <br />\nAdv <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n不過如果產能問題能夠克服的話，這個「異形 OLED」螢幕將會令手機做到三邊甚至四邊都有窄邊框，最終的製成品會十分漂亮，所以一般會用作高階旗艦手機之中，例如 iPhone 8，至於 S8 那種 edge-to-edge 螢幕，最終會向下流，獲入門級和中階手機使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/113458_80acf056d7a363b3e373d3676a91f014.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F113458_80acf056d7a363b3e373d3676a91f014.jpg&h=e1861115&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40bee5d7e221fe8ffbd5d42bc44b74d4b6ec3573","tid":351366,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T06:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88820701e86fb0d4076bf1a46b200275a62386a6","tid":351366,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:52:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56ecd3f78be247bdd3bc75b9c16ddbecacb3ea50","tid":351366,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"異型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肉酸到"},{"pid":"96e0c400298bfd9bce55aa8cdf6fa5798748b86e","tid":351366,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>異型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肉酸到</blockquote><br />\n咪又係大賣"},{"pid":"ce78e961068de709bae4547bc30986ae9f9bf233","tid":351366,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:04:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>技術唔成烹就推出<br />\n<br />\napple 已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n烹你老母"},{"pid":"f0a7c99258391e9e29218ecb0e03fd65dfbabf7d","tid":351366,"uid":62947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"突登cut撚走個mon一忽仲要比貴d<br />\ncock ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e7a352d01493fac2c343f9fb0f758626133c4a","tid":351366,"uid":69289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:14:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>突登cut撚走個m